data.name: LogicTargetModel
desc: The properties of this service correspond to the similar named attributes and subelements of the XML element chart2:increment in the chart2 file format.

types.name: CoordinateSystems
desc: not BOUND nor CONSTRAINED in terms of Listener notifications, each element in the sequence must implement the service com.sun.star.chart2.CoordinateSystem

types.name: LogicTargetModels
desc: MAYBEVOID, not BOUND nor CONSTRAINED in terms of Listener notifications, each element in the sequence must implement the service com.sun.star.chart2.LogicTargetModel.

properties.name: ID
desc: identifies an instance of this service within one chart document.

properties.name: LegendID
desc: identifies an instance of the service com.sun.star.chart2.LegendModel within one chart document.
that instance is used to automatically calculate missing properties
